  "content": "<div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\"><blockquote><p><span>Plunge into the action-packed universe of Capsule Heroes, a unique 3v3 PvP brawler that blends intense combat with strategic depth, </span><strong>developed by Endless Clouds.</strong></p></blockquote><p><span>Curious about what Capsule Heroes is? Read this </span><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes\" rel=\"\">article</a><span>.</span></p><div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\"><div class=\"container-IpPqBD\"><form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" class=\"form form-M5sC90\" novalidate=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/capsule-heroes-questions\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/capsule-heroes-questions\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/capsule-heroes-questions\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\"><div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\"><div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative flexAuto-Bzdrdy pc-reset\"><input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\"></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button></div><div id=\"error-container\"></div></form><div class=\"animationWrapper-QRL6aQ\"></div></div></div></div><h3 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Why are you making Capsule Heroes?<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§why-are-you-making-capsule-heroes\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/132541105/why-are-you-making-capsule-heroes\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h3><p><span>During the </span><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-14#%C2%A7engineering-update\" rel=\"\">game jam</a><span>, Capsule Heroes showed incredible promise. Internally everyone had a blast playing the game and we simply couldn’t throw it away.</span></p><div data-component-name=\"VideoEmbedPlayer\" id=\"media-b1b3a6b2-70fa-4505-963d-cad4527a1ff8\" class=\"videoScrollTarget-SzB20Y\"><div class=\"videoEmbed-_FycLU\"><div role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Video player\" class=\"with-preview full-width video-player-with-background video-player-wrapper full-width\"><div class=\"video-player video-player video-player-with-background videoPlayer-vlcedM\"><video controlslist=\"nodownload\" poster=\"https://substack-video.s3.amazonaws.com/video_upload/post/132541105/b1b3a6b2-70fa-4505-963d-cad4527a1ff8/transcoded-00001.png?refresh=Fri Jul 11 2025 17:07:28 GMT+0100 (British Summer Time)\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" class=\"video-P2qgwZ\" src=\"blob:https://endlessclouds.substack.com/9576b933-b686-4411-a0e9-7cb7c1a8f938\"></video><div class=\"pencraft pc-position-absolute pc-reset buttonContainer-tH3LP9 video-player-button\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"r\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft media-XfKJl4 size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt rounded-SYxRdz\" style=\"width: 56px; height: 56px;\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"Play\" class=\"videoIcon-pEKkgy\" style=\"stroke: none;\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M3.35866 16C2.58101 16 2 15.4101 2 14.4447V1.55531C2 0.598883 2.58101 0 3.35866 0C3.75196 0 4.10056 0.134078 4.54749 0.393296L15.1575 6.54302C15.9531 7.00782 16.3106 7.39218 16.3106 8C16.3106 8.61676 15.9531 9.00112 15.1575 9.45698L4.54749 15.6067C4.10056 15.8659 3.75196 16 3.35866 16Z\"></path></g></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><p><span>The game is much simpler </span><strong>to develop</strong><span> </span><strong>and less resource intensive </strong><span>than Treeverse. It also has the potential to start generating revenue for the company much earlier. Successfully shipping this game will establish Endless Clouds as a reputable and trustworthy game studio.</span></p><p>Furthermore, despite being one of the few NFT projects that have a treasury to last us through a continued bear, it’s important to not get complacent and to start generating revenue as fast as possible.</p><h3 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Doesn’t this take away focus from Treeverse?<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§doesnt-this-take-away-focus-from-treeverse\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/132541105/doesnt-this-take-away-focus-from-treeverse\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h3><p>The effect is not entirely negligible, however after thoughtful consideration, we are confident that the benefits far outweigh any potential downsides.</p><p>We’ve been building for almost 2 years and one of the counterintuitive lessons we’ve learned as founders is that simply adding more people does not speed up development time, especially before the mass production phase of the game. Ironically having too many people work on the product before mass production slows down development instead.</p><p><span>The development speed of Treeverse has been significantly faster in the last few months than all of last year when we had 50+ people working on it. And you can see this in our </span><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/\" rel=\"\">monthly updates</a><span>.</span></p><p><span>Treeverse is a big game, and we aren’t going to rush it, it will take time \"</span><strong>A delayed game is eventually good, but a rushed game is forever bad</strong><span>.\" — this helps us still deliver a fun and competitive game whilst we continue working on the development of Treeverse.</span></p><h3 class=\"header-anchor-post\">But, ser, what about my NFTs?<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§but-ser-what-about-my-nfts\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/132541105/but-ser-what-about-my-nfts\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h3><p>Every NFT we have will play a role in Capsule Heroes, enhancing the interconnectedness of our projects. It is not one NFT, for one project. But one NFT, for all.</p><p><span>Does this mean you will get Plots in Capsule Heroes? No. Not exactly. The Treeverse Plots NFT will represent a new feature yet to be determined. We have a thread next week going more in detail with a change to one of our collections to better illustrate this. Do you have suggestions? Let us know on </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/endlessclouds\" rel=\"\">Discord</a><span>!</span></p><p>Our characters have been modelled with Timeless integration in mind. As you can see examples #8808 &amp; #8570 here:</p><div data-component-name=\"VideoEmbedPlayer\" id=\"media-dc246206-a7d7-43a3-95b5-fb1a0d4a848d\" class=\"videoScrollTarget-SzB20Y\"><div class=\"videoEmbed-_FycLU\"><div role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Video player\" class=\"with-preview full-width video-player-with-background video-player-wrapper full-width\"><div class=\"video-player video-player video-player-with-background videoPlayer-vlcedM\"><video controlslist=\"nodownload\" poster=\"https://substack-video.s3.amazonaws.com/video_upload/post/132541105/dc246206-a7d7-43a3-95b5-fb1a0d4a848d/transcoded-00002.png?refresh=Fri Jul 11 2025 17:07:28 GMT+0100 (British Summer Time)\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" class=\"video-P2qgwZ\" src=\"blob:https://endlessclouds.substack.com/0acdd074-a294-40a8-82a6-ae463425c24d\"></video><div class=\"pencraft pc-position-absolute pc-reset buttonContainer-tH3LP9 video-player-button\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"r\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft media-XfKJl4 size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt rounded-SYxRdz\" style=\"width: 56px; height: 56px;\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"Play\" class=\"videoIcon-pEKkgy\" style=\"stroke: none;\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M3.35866 16C2.58101 16 2 15.4101 2 14.4447V1.55531C2 0.598883 2.58101 0 3.35866 0C3.75196 0 4.10056 0.134078 4.54749 0.393296L15.1575 6.54302C15.9531 7.00782 16.3106 7.39218 16.3106 8C16.3106 8.61676 15.9531 9.00112 15.1575 9.45698L4.54749 15.6067C4.10056 15.8659 3.75196 16 3.35866 16Z\"></path></g></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><p></p><div><hr></div><p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://endlessclouds.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Endless Clouds Updates&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/?utm_source